BTW, I'm the one who made bmp2nes, a very very long time ago, and yes, it is lame. I made a better (windows) tool, that lets you select the colors, also some time ago. You can grab it <a href="http://www.nesstuff.kit.net/nestc.jpg" class="postlink">here</a>. Be sure to right click and use the "save link/target as" option, and rename the extension from "jpg" to "rar", so you can open and decompress it. My crappy server will not allow rar files. I've been using this for a while.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=95">tokumaru</a> — Wed May 24, 2006 2:29 pm</p><hr />
